%info
Minimal DPDK echo/loopback module made with FastClick.

Receives packets on a DPDK port and sends them back with swapped Ethernet
source and destination addresses using EtherMirror. Uses cores 0-7.

With the FastClick dependency, it will build itself.

Usage:
  %import@dut fastclick-echo

%script deps=fastclick sudo=true
click --dpdk -l 0-7 -a ${self:0:pci} -- -e "FromDPDKDevice(0, PROMISC true) -> EtherMirror -> ToDPDKDevice(0);"
